    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into a dependable ride that's ready for all your adventures! This vehicle has been well-cared for and is in good condition, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. While you'll see some light, expected signs of previous use, it has been maintained beautifully and is ready to hit the road today!",
